short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A new tab becomes a minimal space for note taking and lists

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension replaces new tabs with a blank space where you can add any text items. Use it as a simple, clean and minimal space for you to do your writing, copy and paste something to keep for later or keep links, emojis or other text-based things you regularly use. Your information syncs over your gmail account, but is private to you and not stored anywhere else.
